{
  "stem": "9878.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They put a stamp on my passs-- they gave me a pass-- and they took off my lapels from the army [INAUDIBLE], because I didn't have any clothes.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they send me to Stalingrad to work in a factory where they're building tanks.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Meanwhile, your brother-in-law was older?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother-in-law was older.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was taken into the army.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they asked him what kind of profession he is.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He told them that I am a tailor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So a tailor, they didn't want to send to the-- in the-- to get killed on the front with a punishment on the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took him special to a different brigade.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they made him to work for the generals, for their wives, to make coats.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he did not go in the-- in the front.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was standing there, and he was there already in Bryansk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was in Stalingrad, and they sent me into Stalingrad to work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I'll make a long story short what happened.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In 1946, I joined a Polish organization, Polish organization.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It means Organization of the Polish Patriot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because even so the Russians forced on me the Russian citizenship, because I was considered a Pole because I was born in Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I did not want to stay in Russia, in my hometown.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I figured because I received letters from my hometown that Ukrainians are killing Jews, especially who want to take away the houses.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "For a dollar, for two, they'll kill them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And once he's killed, nobody is to ask for the house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The Russians are not going to take it away from them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They are going to give them as an inheritance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I decided, my life, I worked very hard for it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm not going back to my hometown.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
